    public final class SnomedRefSetSearchRequestBuilder
extends SnomedSearchRequestBuilder<SnomedRefSetSearchRequestBuilder,com.b2international.snowowl.snomed.core.domain.refset.SnomedReferenceSets>
    Builder class to build requests responsible for searching SNOMED CT reference sets. This class should be instantiated from the corresponding static method on the central SnomedRequests class. Filter methods restrict the results set returned from the search requests; what passes the filters will be returned as part of the pageable resultset.
    Since:
    4.5
